     H            Y.
      ** GDGR75 ********************************************
      *  GET ASJ PT ORDER UPPER LIMIT DATE MULTI RATE      *
      *                                                    *
      * T.SAKASHITA 2013.APL.29                            *
      ******************************************************
     FGDGPP75 IF  E           K        DISK
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80K@DATE
     I                                        1   40K@YY
     I                                        5   60K@MM
     I                                        7   80K@DD
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@DATE  8
     C                     PARM           P@RATE  5
      *
     C                     MOVE P@DATE    K@DATE
     C                     MOVE '00000'   P@RATE
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@YY    40
     C                     KFLD           K@MM    20
     C                     KFLD           K@DD    20
      *
     C           KEY       CHAINGDGPP75              88
     C           *IN88     IFEQ '0'
     C           GNSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     SETON                     88
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C           *IN88     IFEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE GNRATE    P@RATE
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
